            "id": "20260428A080CD00",
            "title": "英特尔残次CPU遭抢购，贡献Q1高毛利！CPU这么缺？| 0428",
            "image": "https://inews.gtimg.com/om_ls/OzcLPX1pp2UyLHsikOmgPRYvVzKe9hRQfPpJFaAZphTVwAA_870492/0",
            "link": "https://new.qq.com/rain/a/20260428A080CD00",
            "author": "名扬四海",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-28 20:37:07",
            "description": "<div class=\"rich_media_content\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;display:flex;color:#999999;align-items:center\"><svg height=\"1.4em\" viewbox=\"0 0 18 18\" width=\"1.4em\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><mask id=\"exclamation-mask\"><rect fill=\"white\" height=\"16\" width=\"16\"></rect><path d=\"M8 3.5a1 1 0 0 1 1 1v4a1 1 0 1 1-2 0v-4a1 1 0 0 1 1-1zM8 12a1 1 0 1 0 0-2 1 1 0 0 0 0 2z\" fill=\"black\"></path></mask><circle cx=\"8\" cy=\"8\" fill=\"#999999\" mask=\"url(#exclamation-mask)\" r=\"8\"></circle></svg> 该图片使用了AI生成技术</span><p><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"qnt-img-img qnr-img-lazy-load-img qnr-img-lazy-load-img-placeholder\" data-src=\"https://inews.gtimg.com/om_bt/O1ep7vMqzLSHQZRiIFgz9BndSopKDkV9BCGh5w71isdcgAA/1000\" src=\"https://inews.gtimg.com/om_bt/O1ep7vMqzLSHQZRiIFgz9BndSopKDkV9BCGh5w71isdcgAA/1000\" style=\"border-radius:6px;width:100%;height:100%\"/></p> <p data-check-id=\"518334\"><span style=\"color:rgb(164, 29, 29);font-size:20px;font-weight:700\">一、当日行情分析</span><br/></p><p class=\"text-sm-title\" data-check-id=\"493200\" label=\"小标题\">1、市场观察</p><p data-check-id=\"323642\">A股三大股指今日集体震荡走弱，盘中未见有效反弹。收盘方面，上证指数跌0.19%，勉强守住10日均线；深证成指跌1.10%；创业板指跌1.43%，创业板指日线已走出四连阴。</p><p data-check-id=\"642562\">成交方面，沪深京三市成交额约2.55万亿元，较上一交易日缩量约543亿元，呈持续萎缩态势，显示此前预判的节前交投清淡效应已开始兑现。个股层面，涨停个股共77只（含部分ST标的），跌停54只，局部风险仍在加速出清。</p><p data-check-id=\"967298\">市场调整主要由多因素叠加共振所致：一季报披露进入最后冲刺阶段，业绩\"地雷\"集中引爆；\"五一\"小长假临近，假日期间海外市场波动、地缘政治等不确定性因素令资金倾向于持币过节，存量博弈加剧；短期大概率延续震荡磨底格局。</p><p class=\"text-sm-title\" data-check-id=\"571599\" label=\"小标题\">连板股题材梳理</p><p class=\"text-sm-title\" data-check-id=\"386930\" label=\"小标题\"><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"qnt-img-img qnr-img-lazy-load-img qnr-img-lazy-load-img-placeholder\" data-src=\"https://inews.gtimg.com/om_bt/OQyw4JKscRybfJYpYu_AsrNPX7IvLb_eWQQFrovJNwDYwAA/641\" src=\"https://inews.gtimg.com/om_bt/OQyw4JKscRybfJYpYu_AsrNPX7IvLb_eWQQFrovJNwDYwAA/641\" style=\"border-radius:6px;width:100%;height:100%\"/></p><p class=\"text-sm-title\" data-check-id=\"127949\" label=\"小标题\">趋势股板块特征</p><p class=\"img-center-box\" data-check-id=\"634144\"><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"qnt-img-img qnr-img-lazy-load-img qnr-img-lazy-load-img-placeholder\" data-src=\"https://inews.gtimg.com/om_bt/OIMLK-FDNMcCUc9F6QeN5u0ei7STqn9V14l5WVQhMWI4IAA/641\" src=\"https://inews.gtimg.com/om_bt/OIMLK-FDNMcCUc9F6QeN5u0ei7STqn9V14l5WVQhMWI4IAA/641\" style=\"border-radius:6px;width:100%;height:100%\"/></p><p class=\"text-sm-title\" data-check-id=\"359147\" label=\"小标题\">2、国内宏观：政治局会议召开，一季报喜忧交织</p><p class=\"text-sm-title\" data-check-id=\"133446\" label=\"小标题\"><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"qnt-img-img qnr-img-lazy-load-img qnr-img-lazy-load-img-placeholder\" data-src=\"https://inews.gtimg.com/om_bt/OLhVFfPLoq5cGU_IWW-ockQ91stWmLxopbANxG43A2np4AA/641\" src=\"https://inews.gtimg.com/om_bt/OLhVFfPLoq5cGU_IWW-ockQ91stWmLxopbANxG43A2np4AA/641\" style=\"border-radius:6px;width:100%;height:100%\"/></p><p class=\"text-sm-title\" data-check-id=\"304744\" label=\"小标题\">3、美联储 2026 年 4 月 FOMC 议息会议</p><p class=\"text-sm-title\" data-check-id=\"995660\" label=\"小标题\"><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"qnt-img-img qnr-img-lazy-load-img qnr-img-lazy-load-img-placeholder\" data-src=\"https://inews.gtimg.com/om_bt/O2Voa8cckM93So41fT7XqtiP2ZjpVpiJJpCvikG9AHP5QAA/641\" src=\"https://inews.gtimg.com/om_bt/O2Voa8cckM93So41fT7XqtiP2ZjpVpiJJpCvikG9AHP5QAA/641\" style=\"border-radius:6px;width:100%;height:100%\"/></p><p class=\"text-sm-title\" data-check-id=\"635500\" label=\"小标题\">4、日央行鹰派转向在即？</p><p data-check-id=\"687364\">周二，日本央行将目标利率维持在0.75%不变，符合市场预期。不过这是近十年来分期最大的一次议息。</p><p data-check-id=\"228204\">投票结果显示，本次利率决定以6:3的投票比例通过，此前3月的投票比例为8比1。其中，日本央行审议委员中川顺子、高田创和田村直树三位支持加息，提议将利率目标从0.75%上调至1.0%。理由是中东紧张局势加剧，海外价格风险显著上行，需提前应对通胀压力。</p><p data-check-id=\"623760\">日央行行长植田和男发表“鹰”式讲话，若通胀风险兑现或加剧、且经济下行风险可控，就可能加息；即便<!-- -->霍尔木兹海峡<!-- -->关闭，也将依其对经济物价的影响评估后决定是否加息。 他明确，央行今日决议是忽略暂时性供给冲击通胀，但若冲击引发第二轮通胀效应，就必须加息。</p><p class=\"img-center-box\" data-check-id=\"679800\"><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"qnt-img-img qnr-img-lazy-load-img qnr-img-lazy-load-img-placeholder\" data-src=\"https://inews.gtimg.com/om_bt/O-BdgKA9QyeG7CcCkfS6dSjmRlH1LdtMNakATZEvdrspsAA/641\" src=\"https://inews.gtimg.com/om_bt/O-BdgKA9QyeG7CcCkfS6dSjmRlH1LdtMNakATZEvdrspsAA/641\" style=\"border-radius:6px;width:100%;height:100%\"/></p><p class=\"text-sm-title\" data-check-id=\"717446\" label=\"小标题\">5、废弃 CPU 遭市场场抢购 </p><p class=\"img-center-box\" data-check-id=\"763941\"><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"qnt-img-img qnr-img-lazy-load-img qnr-img-lazy-load-img-placeholder\" data-src=\"https://inews.gtimg.com/om_bt/OXExbPvSmvlcjqFZQXktyZm5PzqSbRKXAtdn-HSpaMTxcAA/641\" src=\"https://inews.gtimg.com/om_bt/OXExbPvSmvlcjqFZQXktyZm5PzqSbRKXAtdn-HSpaMTxcAA/641\" style=\"border-radius:6px;width:100%;height:100%\"/></p><p class=\"text-big-title\" data-check-id=\"338871\" label=\"大标题\">二、专栏回顾</p><p class=\"text-sm-title\" data-check-id=\"782235\" label=\"小标题\">1、<span dt-eid=\"\" dt-params=\"\"><span class=\"qnt-link\"><span class=\"qnt-link-text\">利通电子</span></span></span></p><p class=\"text-sm-title\" data-check-id=\"321205\" label=\"小标题\"><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"qnt-img-img qnr-img-lazy-load-img qnr-img-lazy-load-img-placeholder\" data-src=\"https://inews.gtimg.com/om_bt/ONlEU95ULCt_tmkykWAH5yCoGHww1wH37gMbK8PMklGNIAA/641\" src=\"https://inews.gtimg.com/om_bt/ONlEU95ULCt_tmkykWAH5yCoGHww1wH37gMbK8PMklGNIAA/641\" style=\"border-radius:6px;width:100%;height:100%\"/></p><p class=\"text-sm-title\" data-check-id=\"863811\" label=\"小标题\"><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"qnt-img-img qnr-img-lazy-load-img qnr-img-lazy-load-img-placeholder\" data-src=\"https://inews.gtimg.com/om_bt/O_bAhoAu6_E4U6ZaIDJGDpdnDK0ZwcS8DIY6oN059IqCcAA/641\" src=\"https://inews.gtimg.com/om_bt/O_bAhoAu6_E4U6ZaIDJGDpdnDK0ZwcS8DIY6oN059IqCcAA/641\" style=\"border-radius:6px;width:100%;height:100%\"/><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"qnt-img-img qnr-img-lazy-load-img qnr-img-lazy-load-img-placeholder\" data-src=\"https://inews.gtimg.com/om_bt/OoPEKTCuJH5Zb5I10