r-radius:6px;width:100%;height:100%\"/></p><p class=\"text-sm-title\" data-check-id=\"329052\" label=\"小标题\">2、比特微借壳？</p><p class=\"img-center-box\" data-check-id=\"757935\"><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"qnt-img-img qnr-img-lazy-load-img qnr-img-lazy-load-img-placeholder\" data-src=\"https://inews.gtimg.com/om_bt/Om8cLt2eCj16I5pUFYg8jY6FPG2PeJdq8heyXeb2IaYygAA/641\" src=\"https://inews.gtimg.com/om_bt/Om8cLt2eCj16I5pUFYg8jY6FPG2PeJdq8heyXeb2IaYygAA/641\" style=\"border-radius:6px;width:100%;height:100%\"/><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"qnt-img-img qnr-img-lazy-load-img qnr-img-lazy-load-img-placeholder\" data-src=\"https://inews.gtimg.com/om_bt/OQevHKOIHdaVA6ZujOJejHokp_70STjoUZV4WEbW-RYXwAA/641\" src=\"https://inews.gtimg.com/om_bt/OQevHKOIHdaVA6ZujOJejHokp_70STjoUZV4WEbW-RYXwAA/641\" style=\"border-radius:6px;width:100%;height:100%\"/><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"qnt-img-img qnr-img-lazy-load-img qnr-img-lazy-load-img-placeholder\" data-src=\"https://inews.gtimg.com/om_bt/OVt-VY6UGUJWEmwkH-hjBZOfHhQdJgga-Zm6UD9rn-MsEAA/641\" src=\"https://inews.gtimg.com/om_bt/OVt-VY6UGUJWEmwkH-hjBZOfHhQdJgga-Zm6UD9rn-MsEAA/641\" style=\"border-radius:6px;width:100%;height:100%\"/></p><p class=\"img-center-box\" data-check-id=\"550712\"><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"qnt-img-img qnr-img-lazy-load-img qnr-img-lazy-load-img-placeholder\" data-src=\"https://inews.gtimg.com/om_bt/OYpSh6IIcUAHUTwQXQAO5nCsnmeO8a7cW8yQl0K6nsUBgAA/641\" src=\"https://inews.gtimg.com/om_bt/OYpSh6IIcUAHUTwQXQAO5nCsnmeO8a7cW8yQl0K6nsUBgAA/641\" style=\"border-radius:6px;width:100%;height:100%\"/><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"qnt-img-img qnr-img-lazy-load-img qnr-img-lazy-load-img-placeholder\" data-src=\"https://inews.gtimg.com/om_bt/Oyt-evX93dO1fGFYxip47HTrQCjlT4xYgrdjFD7lVqKMIAA/641\" src=\"https://inews.gtimg.com/om_bt/Oyt-evX93dO1fGFYxip47HTrQCjlT4xYgrdjFD7lVqKMIAA/641\" style=\"border-radius:6px;width:100%;height:100%\"/></p><p class=\"img-center-box\" data-check-id=\"373948\"><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"qnt-img-img qnr-img-lazy-load-img qnr-img-lazy-load-img-placeholder\" data-src=\"https://inews.gtimg.com/om_bt/O2Omfz28Da1RKcby3Wvkg4l7kKr2nBfv1vjNyJKP_Bxm4AA/641\" src=\"https://inews.gtimg.com/om_bt/O2Omfz28Da1RKcby3Wvkg4l7kKr2nBfv1vjNyJKP_Bxm4AA/641\" style=\"border-radius:6px;width:100%;height:100%\"/></p><p data-check-id=\"729376\"><strong>特别声明：</strong></p><p data-check-id=\"250952\"><strong>本文有音频解读，可咨询虎子哥；</strong></p><p data-check-id=\"466499\"><strong>文中股票仅为投资逻辑，无任何买卖建议。</strong></p></div>",
